source.query:
select 
id codigo,
contract_id contratoId,
policy_id policyId,
`description` descripcion,
`code` codigoDeVehiculo,
color,
chassis,
plate patente,
`year` anio,
vtv_due_date fechaVencimientoVTV,
cardoc_due_date fechaVencimientoDocument,
warranty_up_to_km garantiaHastaKm,
warranty_up_to_date fechaActualizadaGarantia,
warranty_state garantiaEstado,
is_fleet_owner isPropietarioFlota,
last_km ultimoKilometraje,
last_km_origin ultimoKilometrajeOrigen,
last_km_date fechaUltimoKm,
service_last_km servicioUltimoKm,
service_origin origenServicio,
case when year(service_last_date)<1990 then null else service_last_date end ultimaFechaServicio,
condition_type tipoCondicion,
category_client categoriaCliente,
group_category_client grupoCategoriaCliente ,
fuel_card_number numeroTarjetaCombustible,
toll_card_number numeroTarjetaPeaje,
has_circulation_documents tieneDocumentoCirculacion,
insurance_ammount montoSeguro,
version_id versionID,
vehicle_state_id vehiculoEstadoID,
client_structure_id clienteEstructuraID,
insurance_id seguroID,
gps_provider_id proveedorGpsId,
has_duplicated_key tieneClaveDuplicado,
gps_vehicle_number numeroGPS,
gps_detail detalleGPS,
gps_ammount gpsMonto,
vtv_last_date ultimaFechaVTV,
duplicated_key_date fechaClaveDuplicada,
vtv_last_city_id ultimaCiudadVTVID,
plate_city_id patenteCuidadID,
gps_is_visible gpsIsVisible,
owner_name propietario,
owner_contact_id propietarioContactoID,
maintenance_plan_id planMantenimientoID,
leasing_duedate arrendamientoFechaVencimiento,
rto_due_date fechaDeRetiro,
vtv_km_expiration kmVencimientoVTV,
fuel_provider proveedorCombustible,
service_last_task_id UltimaTareaID,
insurance_start_date fechaInicioSeguro,
send_expiration_mailing ,
hansa_code codigoHansa,
last_expiration_check fechaUltimaComparacion,
vtv_caba_text vtvCabaTexto,
infoauto_price precioInfoauto,
infoauto_price_date fechaPrecioInfoAuto

from vehicles

SELECT 
c.id codigo,
c.fantasy_name nombre,
c.business_name empresa,
c.contact_id,
cg.name grupo,
c.classification clasificacion,
c.first_credit_limit primerLimiteDeCredito,
c.second_credit_limit segundoLimiteDeCredito,
ot.name tipoOperacion,
it.name tipoComprobante,
ct.name tipoCliente,
cst.name estadoCliente
FROM clients c
left join client_types ct on ct.id = c.client_type_id
left join invoice_types it on it.id = c.operation_type_id
left join operation_types ot on ot.id = c.operation_type_id
left join client_state_types cst on cst.id = c.client_state_type_id
left join client_groups cg on cg.id = c.client_group_id

select 
c.id codigo,
c.name nombre,
ct.name tipoContrato
from contracts c
left join contract_types ct on ct.id = c.id

select 
c.id codigo,
c.name nombre,
c.description descripcion,
s.name seccionNombre 
from categories c
left join sections s on s.id = c.section_id

select 
t.id codigo,
t.name nombre,
t.description descripcion,
category_id codigoCategoria
from tasks t

select 
wo.id codigo,
name nombre,
state estado,
wo.deleted_at fechaEliminacion,
wo.created_at fechaCreacion,
wo.updated_at fechaActualizacion,
hansa_Code hansaCode,
wo.work_order_type_id codigoTipoOrdenTrabajo,
work_order_origin_id codigoOrdenTrabajoOriginal,
reason razon,
internal_code codigoInterno,
number numero,
plate patente,
contract_id codigoContrato,
km,
is_estimated estimada,
work_order_expense_type_id codigoTipoGasto,
user_id codigoUsuario,
freshdesk_code codigoTicket,
vwo.vehicle_id codigoVehiculo
from work_orders wo
left join vehicles_work_orders vwo on vwo.work_order_id = wo.id

source.sqlReaderQuery:
select 
t.codigo,
ot.id workOrderId,
ta.id tareaId,
costoPersonal,
costoMaterial,
costoTotal,
costoPersonalSinIva,
costoMaterialSinIva,
costoTotalSinIva,
descuentoPersonal,
decuentoMaterial,
decuentoTotal,
t.fechaCreacion,
fechaUltimaActualizacion

from stg.OrdenTrabajoTareas t
left join whs.dimOrdenesTrabajo ot on ot.codigo = t.codigoWorkOrder
left join whs.dimTareas ta on ta.codigo = t.codigoTarea

source.query:
SELECT id, 
UPPER(TRIM(REPLACE(REPLACE(SUBSTRING_INDEX(name, ',', 1),'[',''),'''',''))) AS  name
from status_table
